{"tid":1953580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男客剉咧等！歌舞伎町爆十多人染疫　多為風俗店小姐","createTime":"2020-04-01T08:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T09:10:19.000Z","uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5bcde4d105e362ebce082e80c58f43afe53cdf","tid":1953580,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"東京新宿歌舞伎町近日爆出有十多人感染武漢肺炎，且多數是與男客有親密接觸的風俗店小姐。但因區內小姐和男客往往不願意配合疫調，日媒今透露實際確診人數可能更多。<br />\n<br />\n日本《讀賣新聞》今（1日）援引相關人士消息指出，新宿區武漢肺炎確診人數自3月中開始就突然暴增，目前已有十多人染疫，且患者多為風俗店小姐和男客。但確診者是少數願意配合疫調的，多數小姐和客人仍不願意配合。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，新宿區區長吉住健一還罕見地呼籲民眾，「謹慎」前往歌舞伎町相關店鋪消費。 <br />\n<br />\n香港呢？"},{"pid":"9a563af0249b673bb7284a9a71647d829d73fcce","tid":1953580,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"日本仔邊敢搞飛田呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fab8a567e520dfdac9ce5c06afcbfec65f4e5d","tid":1953580,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:58:52.000Z","msg":"分分鐘AV 都要停產，世界末日"},{"pid":"e4df04ef887fd997c0ac45b515b21c37c1113f52","tid":1953580,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a563af0249b673bb7284a9a71647d829d73fcce","tid":1953580,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"日本仔邊敢搞飛田呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"飛田 大阪"},{"pid":"c6be12ad8c6713b6063b666f25b0cff173d60f8a","tid":1953580,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1fab8a567e520dfdac9ce5c06afcbfec65f4e5d","tid":1953580,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:58:52.0